description:
Change your Amigo's maracas sound effect into a Sonic the Hedgehog Ring sound effect with this item!

This sound effect is included in the Sonic the Hedgehog Costume & Accessories Pack.

Purchasing the Sonic the Hedgehog Costume & Accessories Pack will make this sound effect available for your Amigo in the shop menu.
name: Sonic the Hedgehog Ring Sound Effect
